Additional Terms for AI/LLM Usage:

1. AI/LLM Integration
   - Integration with AI/LLM systems is permitted with proper attribution to the Memory Agent project
   - Usage must comply with the project's data privacy guidelines and security policies
   - Integration must not be used for malicious purposes or applications

2. Model Training
   - Usage of the Software for model training is permitted
   - Training data must comply with data privacy requirements specified in project documentation
   - Models trained using the Software must maintain appropriate safeguards against misuse

3. API Usage
   - API access is subject to rate limiting and security policies
   - Users must implement specified security controls
   - Usage patterns must not compromise system integrity or performance

